summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 34E, page 99, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Comstock Addition, Lots 6 to 10 incl., Block 7, Lots 6 to 8 incl., Block 14, located on the east side of 3rd Ave. W. between W. Highland Drive and line, 2 lots south of W. Lee St., as Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone.
